Sentencas: In present study, Ho2O3 and Dy2O3 doped Bi2O3 composite materials for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells (IT-SOFCs) were investigated.
Titulo: Synthesizing of (Bi2O3)1-x-y(Ho2O3)x( Dy2O3)y Electrolytes for Intermediate-Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: (Bi2O3)(1-x-y)(Ho2O3)(x)(Dy2O3)(y) ternary systems (x = 0.11, 0.13, 0.15 and y = 0.01, 0.03, 0.05, 0.07) were fabricated using conventional solid-state synthesis techniques.
Titulo: Synthesizing of (Bi2O3)1-x-y(Ho2O3)x( Dy2O3)y Electrolytes for Intermediate-Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The samples were characterized by means of X-ray powder diffraction, scanning electron microscopy, energy dispersive X-ray spectroscopy, differential thermal analysis/thermal gravimeter, and the four-point probe technique.
Titulo: Synthesizing of (Bi2O3)1-x-y(Ho2O3)x( Dy2O3)y Electrolytes for Intermediate-Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: X-ray powder diffraction measurements indicated that all samples have the stable fluorite type face centered cubic (fcc) delta-Bi2O3 phase.
Titulo: Synthesizing of (Bi2O3)1-x-y(Ho2O3)x( Dy2O3)y Electrolytes for Intermediate-Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Scanning electron microscopy micrographs of all of the samples showed that grain size distribution was uniform.
Titulo: Synthesizing of (Bi2O3)1-x-y(Ho2O3)x( Dy2O3)y Electrolytes for Intermediate-Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Four-point probe technique measurements showed that the conductivity of the samples increase with increase of temperature.
